15
00:00:34.650 --> 00:00:36.450
No grandpa I apologize

16
00:00:36.450 --> 00:00:37.800
Can I apologize?

17
00:00:37.800 --> 00:00:39.766
Brother Fan is my eyes but I don't know Mount Tai

18
00:00:39.766 --> 00:00:40.850
You adults don't remember villains

19
00:00:40.850 --> 00:00:41.566
Spare me this time

20
00:00:41.566 --> 00:00:44.100
