22
00:00:48.450 --> 00:00:50.100
Forgive you

23
00:00:50.200 --> 00:00:51.150
Go back.

24
00:00:52.250 --> 00:00:53.550
Just being polite to you.

25
00:00:54.366 --> 00:00:56.266
Fucking ugly

26
00:00:57.083 --> 00:00:58.266
Ugly what ugly

27
00:00:58.600 --> 00:01:00.766
Dad, you lack of string

28
00:01:00.766 --> 00:01:02.333
