29
00:01:02.333 --> 00:01:04.050
Do you know the origin of this Xiao Fan?

30
00:01:04.050 --> 00:01:05.650
Even your grandfather's bodyguard

31
00:01:05.650 --> 00:01:06.900
No match for him

32
00:01:06.966 --> 00:01:08.233
How is that possible?

33
00:01:08.966 --> 00:01:10.683
I'm telling you that's the truth.

34
00:01:10.683 --> 00:01:12.733
I was in the house watching him break in

35
00:01:12.733 --> 00:01:14.766
I thought he was sneaking in

36
00:01:14.766 --> 00:01:16.233
