37
00:01:16.250 --> 00:01:18.600
Your grandfather's tiled guards were all brought down by him

38
00:01:18.600 --> 00:01:20.300
Don't blame me for not warning you.

39
00:01:20.600 --> 00:01:21.966
Make friends with him quickly

40
00:01:21.966 --> 00:01:23.966
Even if your grandfather spared you

41
00:01:23.966 --> 00:01:25.383
I won't forgive you either.

